{
  "chapter": 6,
  "chapter_summary": "第六回\"飞蛾行动\"。多年后，一位长者和一位醉心于兵法的少年在讨论当年轰动天下的飞蛾行动。长者为少年详细解析了铁大爷与丝路先生在八月十五子时发动的第一波攻击——108名弓箭手的\"弓箭作业\"以及随后的一系列陷阱埋伏。少年逐渐领悟到，弓箭攻击只是幌子，真正的杀招是藏在各种意想不到之处的\"丝\"级杀手：藏在马桶中一刀刺穿燕冲霄肛门致死的刺客；藏在灶火中用通红铁条插入吕慎吕密兄弟腹中的杀手；藏在特制桑皮纸灯笼中割下虎丘五杰头颅的伏兵；以及藏在棺材底、纸扎中的刺客，最终取走了程冻和郭温的性命。少年愤怒地指责慕容带人去送死的做法，后突然领悟：飞蛾行动本身就是一场自杀式行动，慕容要让自己\"置之于死地而后生\"，让别人都以为他已死。少年最终说出三个字——\"楚留香\"，暗示这一切与已经死了十几个月的楚留香有着千丝万缕的关系。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "根据最正确的考证，那一次行动是在当年八月十五的子时才开始的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_chang_zhe",
      "text": "根据你的考证，那一次行动真的就叫做飞蛾行动？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 9
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "长者",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "绝对不假。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_chang_zhe",
      "text": "我不信。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "长者",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "飞蛾扑火，本来就是自寻死路。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_chang_zhe",
      "text": "那么你难道要我相信，他们筹划这次行动，为的就是要毁灭自己？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "长者",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "我没有这么说。可是你如果一定要这么想，也没有错。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 21
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_chang_zhe",
      "text": "我不懂你的意思。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "长者",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "那一次行动的真正用意，的确是让人很难想像得到的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 27
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_chang_zhe",
      "text": "那么，铁大爷发动的第一次攻击用的是这种法子？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 51
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "长者",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "是的。他用的就是这种方法，只不过用的就是普通的弓箭，只不过他在街道两旁，一共埋伏了一百零八把强弓，每人配带三十六根雕翎箭，弓箭手都是擅射\"连珠\"的专家，别人射出一箭时，他们已射出三箭！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "长者",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "这一百零八人弯弓射箭，只发出\"蓬\"的一声。从这一点，你大概已经可以想见他们配合之密切，和他们反应之灵敏了！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_chang_zhe",
      "text": "铁大爷和丝路先生为什么不用他们早已埋伏好的那一支奇兵？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "长者",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "你说的是丝士？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_chang_zhe",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "长者",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "这一点你应该能够想得到的。他们的这一支既已埋伏在别人绝对想像不到的隐秘之处，不到必要时，为什么要把自己暴露出来？这一类的埋伏奇兵，不到生死胜负系于一发的时候，是万万不能用的。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 71
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_chang_zhe",
      "text": "可是，我还是觉得用那些弓箭手作第一次攻势的主力，未免太弱了些。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "长者",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "不弱。绝对不弱。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "长者",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "用这批弓箭手作首次攻势，至少先占了三点优势。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_chang_zhe",
      "text": "哪三点？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "长者",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "第一，慕容他们一定也像我们一样，想不到对方会用弓箭手发动攻击，而且在双方还没有对面的时候，就已发动。现在我虽然看得比较清楚，只不过是事后的先见之明而已，当时他们一定会很意外。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "长者",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "第二，弓弦一响，灯光立刻熄灭，表示他们的箭在射出时，就已瞄准了对象。可是被他们攻击的对象，却在一种完全没有防备的情况下，眼前忽然变得一片黑暗，就好像一下子就从亮如白昼的灯火辉煌处，落入万劫不复的黑暗深渊。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 99
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "长者",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "这两点虽然已足够，可是我还是要用第三点来补足：这一百零八位弓箭手，本来至少要对付一百人的，现在却将攻击力全都集合到他们身上。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 103
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_chang_zhe",
      "text": "因为他们要接的并不是三五根箭！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "长者",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_chang_zhe",
      "text": "这么说来，铁大爷这一次攻击完全成功了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "长者",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "其实铁大爷并不是有勇无谋的人，他们要发动的第一次攻击，其实包括了三个独立的程序，弓箭作业，只不过是第一个程序而已。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_chang_zhe",
      "text": "不错，这一个程序，主要并不是为了杀人，而是为了要让对方的阵脚动乱。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 121
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "长者",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "说下去。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_chang_zhe",
      "text": "像丁子灵那样的高手，要避开这种弓箭绝非难事，也许在弓箭声响时，他们就已脱离了攻击区。可是他们的阵脚一乱，在黑暗中闪跃躲避追捕追击，动乱间就难免会落人对方埋伏的陷阱里。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 129
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_chang_zhe",
      "text": "当时情况，是不是这样子的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "长者",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "是的，当时的情况就是这样子的。令人想不到的是，第一个落入陷阱的人，居然是燕冲霄。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 137
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_chang_zhe",
      "text": "你说的是不是那个娶了五个男伶做妾的燕子相公？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 141
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "长者",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "是的。当然就是他。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "长者",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "程冻冷酷谨慎，郭温机警敏捷，两人联手，所向无敌，我相信他们这一生中一定从未有过那种绝望的感觉。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 453,
      "line_end": 455
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_chang_zhe",
      "text": "我相信他们以后也不会有那种感觉了。死人是没有感觉的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 457,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "长者",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "所以一个人活着的时候，就应该好好利用他的思想和感觉，永远不要把自己像条死鱼般吊在那里任人宰割。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 461,
      "line_end": 462
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_chang_zhe",
      "text": "是的。这一点我一定会特别小心。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 465,
      "line_end": 465
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "长者",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "现在你在想什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 469,
      "line_end": 471
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_chang_zhe",
      "text": "我在想，等到灯火再亮起时，那位慕容公子带去的人还会剩下几个？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 473,
      "line_end": 473
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "长者",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "剩下的当然已不多。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 475,
      "line_end": 475
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_chang_zhe",
      "text": "柳明秋一去之后就全无消息，慕容既不问他是否得手，也不去查明他的生死下落，就贸然带着一批人去赴约，而且居然是堂堂皇皇的走进那个根本一无所知的死镇。我认为这种做法不但愚蠢，而且可恶。谁也没有权力要别人陪他去送死。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 477,
      "line_end": 483
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "长者",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "你当然会认为这种做法可恶，我在你这种年纪的时候，也会这么想的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 485,
      "line_end": 487
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_chang_zhe",
      "text": "现在呢？现在你怎么想？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 489,
      "line_end": 489
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "长者",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "你还记不记得他们这次行动被称为什么行动？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 491,
      "line_end": 491
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_chang_zhe",
      "text": "飞蛾行动。难道他们这次行动的目的，就像是飞蛾扑火一样，本来就是要去送死的。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 493,
      "line_end": 497
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_chang_zhe",
      "text": "我明白了。他们这次行动根本就是要去送死的。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 511,
      "line_end": 513
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "长者",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "哦？你认为这个世界上真的有这么多人想死？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 515,
      "line_end": 515
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_chang_zhe",
      "text": "我没有这么想。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 517,
      "line_end": 517
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "长者",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "不想死的人为什么要去送死？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 519,
      "line_end": 519
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_chang_zhe",
      "text": "他们当然另外有目的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 521,
      "line_end": 521
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "长者",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "什么目的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 523,
      "line_end": 523
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_chang_zhe",
      "text": "他们……我的意思并不是说他们，而是说他。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 525,
      "line_end": 527
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "长者",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "我不明白你的意思。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 529,
      "line_end": 529
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
      "listener": "char_chang_zhe",
      "text": "他们是那些去送死的人，他是要那些人去送死的人。他要他们去送死，只因为他另有目的，那些不明不白就死掉的人，也许根本就不知道是怎么回事。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 531,
      "line_end": 534
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_zhe",
      "speaker_name": "长者",
      "listener": "char_shao_nian",
      "text": "你认为是怎么回事呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 6,
      "line_start": 537,
      "line_end": 537
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shao_nian",
      "speaker_name": "少年",
